data.description: This is a beautiful home with a lot of extras! This home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bath, spacious dining room with beautiful hardwood floors. Lots of cabinets in the kitchen. Master bedroom on main level that can accommodate a king size bed and more. As if this is not enough, there is a screen in deck on the back with and additional covered deck in the back yard! You will need to see it to believe it. Huge den downstairs - you would be pleased if you saw this home! House sold as-is.
